{"word":"G269 - ἄμαχος - ámachos - am'-akh-os - Not a brawler","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄμαχος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ámachos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">am'-akh-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Not a brawler</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சண்டை பண்ணாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"not to be withstood, invincible abstaining from fighting"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G3163 - μάχη - máchē - makh'-ay/3163\">G3163</a>; <i>peaceable:</i> - not a brawler.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2313/2313\">G2313</a>, <a href=\"#/G2314/2314\">G2314</a>, <a href=\"#/G269/269\">G269</a>, <a href=\"#/G3163/3163\">G3163</a>, <a href=\"#/G3164/3164\">G3164</a>"}]}